{% set page = 'Kontakt' %}
{% set body_class = 'contact' %}
{% set header_class = '' %}
{% set language = 'sl' %}
{% extends "partials/_layout.twig" %}

{% block content %}
<section class="top_content">
  <div class="container">
    <p>Z uvedbo konsistentne personalizirane komunikacije prek e-pošte, SMS in mobilnih obvestil boste svoje stranke obdržali in pridobili nove ter hkrati povečali moč blagovne znamke. Zveste in zadovoljne stranke pa za vaše podjetje pomenijo dolgotrajno rast prodaje in večji dobiček.</p>
    <p>Kontaktirajte nas in skupaj odkrijmo najboljše možnosti uporabe platforme Kumuluz Crowdsensing, da boste lažje dosegli vaše prodajne cilje.</p>

  </div>
</section>
<section id="contact_form">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-12 col-xl-8">
      <div class="contact-form">
        <h3 class="darkblue">Govorite z našimi strokovnjaki</h3>
        <form method="POST" action="https://sunesis.si/thanks/" name="contact-form" class="row">
          <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="contact-form">
          <input type="hidden" name="itsatrap">
          <div class="col-6 mb-4">

              <label for="fullName" class="col-12 col-form-label">Ime in priimek</label>
              <input type="text" name="fullName" id="fullName" placeholder="Vaše polno ime" value="" maxlength="50" class="form-control">

          </div>
          <div class="col-6 mb-4">

              <label for="company" class="col-12 col-form-label">Podjetje</label>
              <input type="text" name="company" id="company" placeholder="Podjetje" value="" maxlength="50" class="form-control">

          </div>
          <div class="col-6 mb-4">

              <label for="email" class="col-12 col-form-label">Elektronski naslov</label>
              <input type="text" name="email" id="email" placeholder="janeznovak at email" value="" class="form-control">

          </div>
          <div class="col-6 mb-4">

              <label for="phoneNumber" class="col-12 col-form-label">Telefonska številka</label>
              <input type="text" name="phoneNumber" id="phoneNumber" placeholder="+386 41 123 456" value="" class="form-control">

          </div>
          <div class="mb-4 col-12">

              <label for="message" class="col-12 col-form-label">Kako Vam lahko pomagamo?</label>
              <textarea name="message" id="message" placeholder="Vnesite svoje sporočilo..." maxlength="1000" class="form-control"></textarea>
              <small class="ml-auto form-text text-muted">Znakov na voljo: <span>1000</span></small>

          </div>
          <div class="col-12">

              <button class="mt-3 mb-5 button" type="submit">Pošlji poizvedbo</button>

          </div>

        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-12 col-xl-3 offset-xl-1">
      <h3 class="darkblue"><span>Kontaktne informacije</span></h4>
      <h4><span>SUNESIS d.o.o.</span></h4>
      <p class="address">Ulica gledališča BTC 2,<br> Ljubljana, Slovenija <br>PE Ptuj, Osojnikova 3, Ptuj<br>PE Maribor, Beloruska 5, Maribor</p>
      <p class="mt-4">
        e: info@sunesis.si
      </p>
